Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:34.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he broke through\Nthe station gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:35.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kyoraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:36.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:40.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What, he’s here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I’d better head out…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just one Ryoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and as your lieutenant,\NI should suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Nanao…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Old Man Yama’s orders,\Nso it can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t want anyone to think
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that the Ryokas are giving him\Nany more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don’t look so worried…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:10.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a little distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve come far enough,\Nyou foolish Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:42.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the lieutenant\Nand third seat of Squad Eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsufusa Enjoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have chosen the wrong path!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:56.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment I appeared here,\Nthis path came to a dead-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, what’s the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t make a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to be ashamed of.\NThat is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:20.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is the technique of\Nthe great swordsman, Tatsufusa Enjoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So far, not one has defeated--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning,\Ntwo blasts a day was my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I don’t tire even after firing\Nmore than five blasts…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have to thank Yoruichi\Nfor training me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Squad Eight Captain,\NShunsui Kyoraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Eight… Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, how do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nanao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough flower petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Maybe she didn’t hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Enough flower petals!\NCute, cute Nanao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely, lovely Nanao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:21.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time for your skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pass…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What, can’t you get\Nin the groove a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s so indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in a hurry,\Nplease move aside from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t seem like a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If possible…\NI don’t want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… You’ve got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:51.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neither one of us wants to fight.\NBut I can’t let you pass, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there any way\Nyou could just withdraw?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:02.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s have a friendly drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you can’t withdraw,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:19.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you could stop here\Nfor a while at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just for a little while…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, come on…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Minors can’t drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. That’s a problem.\NThat’s no good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:41.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The other captains are on the move too.\NSoon this battle will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So if you could sit out until…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The other captains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ichigo and the others are\Nbeing pursued by the captains as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The situation’s changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoraku, please move out of my way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:31.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is becoming cumbersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You missed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why… How come…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He deflected the first blast\Nwith one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:24.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And since then,\Nhe’s dodged every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why hasn’t a single shot\Nlanded on target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t even have a scratch…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:34.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The last guy said that\Nhe was a lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That should be only two levels\Nbetween him and the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just two levels,\Nand yet so far apart…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:46.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is the captain class on\Nsuch a different level?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop already, I’m sure you realize…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,your skills are certainly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:01.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hard, fast, and for a human,\Nyou have an impressive destructive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, you can’t hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure you can see\Nwhere this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you give up\Nand go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, already…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure you realize…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:39.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are techniques which completely\Nrun out at the point of exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and those you can push beyond that,\Nat the expense of draining your lifeforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks are obviously\Nof the latter type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t say anything rude,\Nso just go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep going like this,\Nyou’ll really die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, what a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:22.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to keep fighting so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:26.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s your purpose?\NWhy did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:31.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My purpose is to save Rukia Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t it just this spring that\Nshe went missing in the human world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s too short.\NIt’s a shallow friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would hardly think\Nthat’s worth risking your life for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true I know nothing about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that it may fall short of\Nbeing worthy of risking my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ichigo wants to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:06.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need any other reason\Nto risk my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw geez, what a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you’re that determined,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then it would be insulting\Nto ask you to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess I’ll have\Nto take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will…defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will probably have to risk my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:45.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Should I survive, this time, I will vow…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:51.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The same promise as that time,\Nin the same words as that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, let’s get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you just standing there, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you were lucky\NI happened to be around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you could have gotten seriously hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re incredibly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d you let those guys\Nbeat you up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you go at it\Nlike the time you saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made a vow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to never use my fist for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a promise I made with Abuelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abu… come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abuelo. It means “Grandpa.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:28.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Oscar Joaquin de la Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What ethnicity is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mestizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s Mexican.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before I came here,\NI was in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Last month when\Nyou introduced yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you said you were from Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:52.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind!\NSay whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I won’t save your hide\Nthe next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that thing you’ve always got\Naround your neck…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s precious…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably more than my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a foreign coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:24.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! There you go again. Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It might belong to one of\Nthat earlier bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hassle…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I’ll get it back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should just throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neither was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in Okinawa,\Nand went to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my parents when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With no other relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was taken in by\Nmy Abuelo in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasutora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a rotten kid,\Nhopelessly spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I relied on my size\Nand if anyone so much as irritated me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would punch them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:43.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who strictly scolded me\Ninto shape was Abuelo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:48.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was truly, hopelessly spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:58.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…on that fateful day,\NI was hopelessly careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:06.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:28.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These wires are awfully thick.\N I don’t think I can break out of these…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for the Chad\Nof Mashiba Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, how does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt enough to\Nmake you want to piss? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So if it hurts, I’m supposed to piss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it’ll be a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:43.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how’s about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know!\NYou value this more than your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:04.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So if you lost this,\Nthen you’ve got to die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So die, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:09.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:56.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those big and strong fists of yours –
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for what purpose\N were you blessed with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Learn about that.\NThis amulet will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Abuelo,\NI grew up to be a decent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:14.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could thank him until\Nmy voice went hoarse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and it still wouldn’t be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:24.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Wha…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way can you break that.\NKick him down--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki of Mashiba Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fishing around\Nin Yokochin’s pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yokochin, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yokochin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it! I told you guys\Nnot to call me that name…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I\Nhave to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:00.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yokochin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me.\NI’d like to call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-An ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:11.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about Sado\Nbefore you even fight us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mock us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:19.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The location is on the second block,\Nunder the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Number of ambulances…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:25.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four, five…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:26.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five ambulances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:28.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!\NDamn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how’s about this, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:38.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stay the same and\Nnot throw any punches for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you throw those punches for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll throw the punches for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re going to stake your life\Nto protect it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then I’ll stake my life\Nto protect it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. It’s a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I can’t lose…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those big and strong fists of yours –
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for what purpose\Nwere you blessed with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:41.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:48.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:22:01.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:08.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:36.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, one of your bells fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:38.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Wait a sec,\NI'll fix it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:40.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you set your hair yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A man's got to look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, you're so talented!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to do your hair, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:45.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, no thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:46.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?